## 2. THREE-LAYER VOTING ENGINE

**RULE:** An order routes to the broker **only if all three layers align**. Any layer **NO** → **block** (no order or bridge returns `success: false` with reason).

### Layer 1 — Behavioral Bias (Initiator)

| Component | Responsibility |
|-----------|----------------|
| **Purpose** | Macro bias: smart money / fundamentals agree before short-vol or directional entry |
| **Python hooks** | `scripts/committee_engine.py` → `LookbackWindow.check_quiver_insider()` |
| **API** | **Quiver Quantitative** — legal corporate insider transactions, short-interest float (when enabled) |
| **Async rule** | **Lookback window:** insider buy OR significant activity within last `lookbackHours` (default 24) — **not** same-second as TV bar |
| **Pine proxy (Phase 1)** | VIX vs SMA (not elevated); SPY/QQQ relative strength rising |
| **Vote** | `layerBehavioral == true` |

### Layer 2 — Structural Liquidity (Dark Pool Gatekeeper)

| Component | Responsibility |
|-----------|----------------|
| **Purpose** | Institutional flow present; ignore retail noise |
| **Python hooks** | `LookbackWindow.check_unusual_whales_dp()`; optional 15-min burst on trigger |
| **API** | **Unusual Whales** — dark pool prints, heavy options sweeps (when enabled) |
| **Pine proxy (Phase 1)** | Volume **> 2σ** above 20-period MA; optional VWAP/structure break; block dead tape (volZ < 0.25) |
| **Vote** | `layerStructural == true` |

### Layer 3 — Statistical Execution (Timing Clock)

| Component | Responsibility |
|-----------|----------------|
| **Purpose** | Exact entry moment; avoid overpaying premium |
| **Pine** | **ATR volatility squeeze:** Bollinger Band inside Keltner Channel compression → release; **AND** MACD line cross up (12/26/9) |
| **Python** | **IV Rank / IV proxy** via VIX regime + ORATS hook (Phase 3) — avoid buying rich premium (IV crush) |
| **IV routing** | `ivRegime` 0=low → long ITM (Phase 4); 1=mid / 2=high → **put_credit_spread** (production) |
| **Vote** | `layerStatistical == true` |

### Committee consensus

```
committeePass = layerBehavioral AND layerStructural AND layerStatistical
entry_fire = committeePass AND macdCrossUp AND liquidityOK
```

