## 9. CURSOR TERMINAL & DEBUG PROTOCOL

When any task involves connectivity or orders:

1. `GET https://spy-options-bridge.onrender.com/health` — expect `version` ≥ 5.5, `configured: true`
2. Read `C:\Users\Shiel\spy-options-bridge\.env` for secrets (do not print secrets to user)
3. Run `.\.venv\Scripts\python.exe scripts\exercise_system.py` or `scripts\scenario_lab.py` from bridge root
4. On failure: read stderr; check Alpaca `403` (position conflict), `401` (secret), unfilled `New` (limit vs market)
5. Git push from `spy-options-bridge` with Git in PATH: `C:\Program Files\Git\bin`
6. User Render deploy: Manual Deploy after push — remind in **one step** only

**Alpaca paper base:** `https://paper-api.alpaca.markets`  
**Data:** `https://data.alpaca.markets`

